  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">Effective date: April 25, 2026 · Last updated: April 25, 2026</p>

  <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
  <p>Pathly ("we", "us", "our") is a job-search management and AI career tool. Our service is operated at the domain where you accessed this page.</p>

  <h2>2. What We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account data:</strong> username, email address, and hashed password (we never store your password in plain text).</li>
    <li><strong>Profile data:</strong> name, phone, location, LinkedIn URL, desired role and location, work authorization — all provided voluntarily.</li>
    <li><strong>Resume content:</strong> text extracted from uploaded resumes, stored to power AI features. Files are stored on our server and not shared.</li>
    <li><strong>Writing samples:</strong> text you paste or upload to calibrate AI writing style.</li>
    <li><strong>Job tracking data:</strong> companies, roles, statuses, notes, and dates you enter.</li>
    <li><strong>Billing data:</strong> subscription status. Payment details are handled by Stripe — we never see or store your card number.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage logs:</strong> server-side structured logs (no analytics SDK, no third-party trackers).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide and improve the Pathly service.</li>
    <li>To generate AI-powered resume profiles and cover letters using your resume text (sent to Anthropic's API).</li>
    <li>To manage your subscription via Stripe.</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your data. We do <strong>not</strong> use your data for advertising.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Anthropic Claude API</strong> — resume text and job data are sent to Anthropic to generate AI content. Anthropic's privacy policy applies to data processed by their API.</li>
    <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — payment processing. Stripe's privacy policy governs billing data.</li>
    <li><strong>The Muse / Remotive</strong> — public job listing APIs used for job search. No personal data is sent to these services.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>Your data is retained for as long as your account is active. You may request full deletion of your account and all associated data at any time via your account settings or by emailing us.</p>

  <h2>6. Canadian Privacy Law (PIPEDA / CASL)</h2>
  <p>We comply with Canada's Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA). You have the right to access, correct, and withdraw consent for the use of your personal information. To exercise these rights, contact us at the email below.</p>

  <h2>7. Security</h2>
  <p>Passwords are hashed using SHA-256. API keys are 48-character random hex tokens. File access is gated behind authentication. We use rate limiting to prevent abuse.</p>

  <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Access or export your data</li>
    <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
    <li>Delete your account and all associated data</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent for AI processing (by deleting your resume text)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@pathly.app">privacy@pathly.app</a>.</p>
